<p>ISMM World Congress on Mountain Medicine 2018 is being hosted by Mountain Medicine Society of Nepal (MMSN) and organized by Mountain Medicine Society of Nepal (MMSN), International Society for Mountain Medicine (ISMM), eurac research and Himalayan Rescue Association, Nepal.</p>

<p><small>This article(and its content) have been developed and presented here solely for informative purpose with contents from ISMM 2018’s official site www.ismm2018.org. </small></p>

<p><br /></p>

