<p><br /><br /></p>
<h2 class="rhre"> Congress Areas</h2>
<p>The 3 day’s Congress will focus on following areas of mountain medicine and high alititude physiology.</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Day 1: Mountain Emergency Medicine</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Day 2: High Altitude Research</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Day 3: Travel Medicine in the Himalayas</p>
  </li>
</ul>

